        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Corporate Accountability Tax Gap Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide for public disclosure of certain information of publicly traded corporations.<p>Directs the Secretary of the Treasury to conduct a study of corporate tax shelter activity.]]></text>
      </summary>
